name: Demon hunters
description: Step into the abyss with Demon Hunters, a captivating NFT collection where fearless warriors arise to combat the encroaching darkness from the depths below. Each intricately designed demon hunter possesses unique abilities and armaments, wielding both traditional and otherworldly weapons to safeguard the metaverse. Unite with the last line of defense as they clash against the malevolent forces, embodying bravery and determination to keep the balance between light and shadow intact.
